cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.AI, cs.CV

The paper proposes a deep learning approach for learning physics models for model-based control, which involves extrapolation from fewer samples and requires physical insight. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.RO (Robotics) and cs.SY (Systems and Control). The paper also involves the use of prior knowledge and physical plausibility, which suggests the categories cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CV (Computer Vision) as possible sub-categories.
